# Operator secrets for tools/generate.py, tools/generate_sdk.py, tools/eval.py.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` (NEVER commit it — `.env` is gitignored) and
# fill in the auth token(s) that match your account. The scripts read
# `.env` from the repo root automatically before running anything that
# needs auth, so you don't have to `export` in every shell.
#
# Pick ONE auth path:
#
# (a) Per-token billing via API key:
#       ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...
#     Get one at https://console.anthropic.com/. Works with both
#     generate.py and generate_sdk.py.
#
# (b) Subscription auth via Claude Pro/Max OAuth:
#       CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=sk-ant-oat01-...
#     Mint with `claude setup-token` (one-time, gives you a 1-year
#     token). Works only with generate_sdk.py.
#
# IMPORTANT — when both are set, the SDK uses ANTHROPIC_API_KEY and
# silently IGNORES CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN (per-token billing
# happens). To use your subscription, leave ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
# unset (or commented out) in this file.

# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...
# CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=sk-ant-oat01-...
